Class Node

java.lang.Object
  objects.Node

public class Node
extends java.lang.Object

Author:
Soroush this is the node object that exists in our binary trie. each node has a left child, right child, ip string, mask string, weight integer and if the prefix is full, a true boolean of isNexthop.
